description: Retrieves information about the status of registering your Amazon Web Services account, IAM, and Amazon Timestream resources so that Amazon Web Services IoT FleetWise can transfer your vehicle data to the Amazon Web Services Cloud. For more information, including step-by-step procedures, see Setting up Amazon Web Services IoT FleetWise.

nested_items.name: customerAccountId
nested_items.description: The unique ID of the Amazon Web Services account, provided at account creation.

nested_items.name: accountStatus
nested_items.description: The status of registering your account and resources. The status can be one of:
REGISTRATION_SUCCESS - The Amazon Web Services resource is successfully registered.
REGISTRATION_PENDING - Amazon Web Services IoT FleetWise is processing the registration request. This process takes approximately five minutes to complete.
REGISTRATION_FAILURE - Amazon Web Services IoT FleetWise can't register the AWS resource. Try again later.

nested_items.name: timestreamRegistrationResponse
nested_items.description: Information about the registered Amazon Timestream resources or errors, if any.

nested_items.name: timestreamDatabaseName
nested_items.description: The name of the Timestream database.

nested_items.name: timestreamTableName
nested_items.description: The name of the Timestream database table.

nested_items.name: timestreamDatabaseArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the Timestream database.

nested_items.name: timestreamTableArn
nested_items.description: The ARN of the Timestream database table.

nested_items.name: registrationStatus
nested_items.description: The status of registering your Amazon Timestream resources. The status can be one of REGISTRATION_SUCCESS, REGISTRATION_PENDING, REGISTRATION_FAILURE.

nested_items.name: errorMessage
nested_items.description: A message associated with a registration error.

nested_items.name: iamRegistrationResponse
nested_items.description: Information about the registered IAM resources or errors, if any.

nested_items.name: roleArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the IAM role to register.

nested_items.name: registrationStatus
nested_items.description: The status of registering your IAM resource. The status can be one of REGISTRATION_SUCCESS, REGISTRATION_PENDING, REGISTRATION_FAILURE.

nested_items.name: errorMessage
nested_items.description: A message associated with a registration error.

nested_items.name: creationTime
nested_items.description: The time the account was registered, in seconds since epoch (January 1, 1970 at midnight UTC time).

nested_items.name: lastModificationTime
nested_items.description: The time this registration was last updated, in seconds since epoch (January 1, 1970 at midnight UTC time).
